ating more than four times the returns of traditional scams.</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 02:43:00 GMT</pubDate><News:Source>Computing</News:Source><News:Image>http://www.bing.com/th?id=ONUT.HkvyhDqcZLw_HgyTs6o6Ig&amp;pid=News</News:Image><News:ImageSize>w={0}&amp;h={1}&amp;c=14</News:ImageSize><News:ImageMaxWidth>702</News:ImageMaxWidth><News:ImageMaxHeight>498</News:ImageMaxHeight></item><item><title>Deepfake interviews: Navigating the growing AI threat in recruitment and organizational security</title><link>http://www.bing.com/news/apiclick.aspx?ref=FexRss&amp;aid=&amp;tid=69ca8eef90064c2fb0e6a1b369bb0849&amp;url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.fastcompany.com%2f91349104%2fdeepfake-interviews-navigating-the-growing-ai-threat-in-recruitment-and-organizational-security&amp;c=17205891524944017033&amp;mkt=en-us</link><description>The breakneck speed of artificial intelligence (AI) technology has fundamentally reshaped how businesses manage recruitment, communication, and information dissemination. Among these developments, ...</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Jun 2025 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate><News:Source>Fast Company</News:Source></item></channel></rss>